\c 58
\s Vatongi vasina kururama ngavaparadzwe
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raDhavhidhi; rwiyo rweMikitami.
\p
\v 1 Munototaura zvakarurama
\s here, imi vane simba, Munotongera vanakomana vavanhu zvakarurama here?
\p
\v 2 Zvirokwazvo, mumwoyo menyu munoita zvakaipa;
\s Munoyerera vanhu pasi pose kumanikidza kwamaoko enyu.
\p
\v 3 Vakaipa vakava vatorwa kubva padumbu ramai;
\s Vanotsauka vachangozvarwa, vachireva nhema.
\p
\v 4 Uturu hwavo hwakafanana nouturu hwenyoka;
\s Vakafanana nechiva chisinganzwi, chinodzivira nzeve yacho;
\p
\v 5 Chisingateereri izwi ren'anga, Kunyange achiimba nouchenjeri hukuru.
\p
\v 6 Ntwari vhumi meixo avo
\s mumuromo mavo;
\s Jehovha gurai meno makuru avana veshumba.
\p
\v 7 Ngavapwe semvura inoyerera; Kana achishumba nemiseve yake,
\s ngaive seyakagurika.
\p
\v 8 Ngavafanane nehozhwa
\s inonyakatika ichipera;
\s Segambamwedzi romukadzi
\s risina kuona zuva.
\p
\v 9 Hari dzenyu dzisati dzanzwa moto neweminzwa,
\s Iye achadzibvisa nachamupupuri nyama igere, nomoto pamwechete.
\p
\v 1 Â° Akarurama achafara kana achiona
\s kutsiva;
\s Achashambidza tsoka dzake
\s muropa ravakaipa.
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo vanhu vachiti, "Zvirokwazvo
\s mubayiro woakarurama uripo; Zvirokwazvo Mwari aripo,
\s anotonga pasi pose."
